# Gemini CLI Ignore File
# Goal: Optimize AI context, save tokens, and secure data.

# --- System & Git ---
.git/
.gitignore
.npmignore
.repomixignore

# --- Dependencies (AI doesn't need to read these files) ---
node_modules/
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

# --- Build & Output ---
dist/
build/
out/
coverage/
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# --- Security (Strictly prohibited for AI access) ---
**/.env*
**/.env.example
.gemini/.env*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.cert
**/secrets/

# --- Media & Assets (Large files without logic code) ---
**/assets/
**/infographics/
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.svg
*.pdf
*.mp4
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# --- Logs & Temp ---
*.log
logs/
temp/
tmp/
.temp/

# --- AI Framework Files ---
# Exclude framework memory from directory scans to prevent session bleed across projects
